  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make tilesets for your games in minutes.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Automatic tileset generation:<br>          <ul class=\"bb_ul\">          <li>Rectangular tilesets<br>          </li><li>Isometric tilesets<br>          </li><li>Hexagonal type A tilesets<br>          </li><li>Hexagonal type B tilesets<br>          </li><li>Platformer tilesets<br>          </li><li>Street/path tilesets<br>          </li></ul></li><li>Resize tile<br></li><li>Select the number of columns in tileset<br></li><li>Change the distance between tiles<br></li><li>Specify the type of blending transitions between tiles (with or without blurring)<br></li><li>Create custom blending masks<br></li><li>Generate a random set of transitions between tiles (from a list of layout masks)<br></li><li>Edit textures (crop textures, create seamless textures)<br></li><li>Replace tile and all its mixes in the finished tileset<br></li><li>Changing tile position in tileset<br></li><li>Selects the background color (transparent for .png)<br></li><li>Saving and loading project .tsg<br></li><li>Saving the finished tileset to .png or .bmp<br></li><li>Exporting the created tiles in single files</li></ul><br>The program generates a set of transitions between tiles from textures (you can choose ready-made textures or upload your own).<br><br>All tiles can be used for commercial purposes.<br><br>Yes, you can save to PNG and use the output from this program in GameMaker, RPG Maker, Construct, AppGameKit, Tiled Map Editor,...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625100/extras/569d79a5634add4763a5f78f73702b0a.avif?t=1772091088\" width=948 height=212 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make tilesets for your games in minutes.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Automatic tileset generation:<br>          <ul class=\"bb_ul\">          <li>Rectangular tilesets<br>          </li><li>Isometric tilesets<br>          </li><li>Hexagonal type A tilesets<br>          </li><li>Hexagonal type B tilesets<br>          </li><li>Platformer tilesets<br>          </li><li>Street/path tilesets<br>          </li></ul></li><li>Resize tile<br></li><li>Select the number of columns in tileset<br></li><li>Change the distance between tiles<br></li><li>Specify the type of blending transitions between tiles (with or without blurring)<br></li><li>Create custom blending masks<br></li><li>Generate a random set of transitions between tiles (from a list of layout masks)<br></li><li>Edit textures (crop textures, create seamless textures)<br></li><li>Replace tile and all its mixes in the finished tileset<br></li><li>Changing tile position in tileset<br></li><li>Selects the background color (transparent for .png)<br></li><li>Saving and loading project .tsg<br></li><li>Saving the finished tileset to .png or .bmp<br></li><li>Exporting the created tiles in single files</li></ul><br>The program generates a set of transitions between tiles from textures (you can choose ready-made textures or upload your own).<br><br>All tiles can be used for commercial purposes.<br><br>Yes, you can save to PNG and use the output from this program in GameMaker, RPG Maker, Construct, AppGameKit, Tiled Map Editor,...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/625100/extras/569d79a5634add4763a5f78f73702b0a.avif?t=1772091088\" width=948 height=212 /></span>",
